*   **Participation Trends:** Refined the dual-axis chart with high-contrast lines and explicit axis labels for "Active Earners" vs "Average Wages."
*   **Standardized Aesthetics:** Applied a unified, professional color palette and the high-contrast dark tooltip theme across all charts.

These new insights provide a much clearer picture of how economic factors influence the daily lives and well-being of the Engagement, Ohio population.

